# Maruko ISP tuning .bin blobs
#
# Pulled from /etc/sensors/*.bin on a known-good Maruko device by
# scripts/maruko_pull_artifacts.sh isp-bins.
#
# Deployed back to /etc/sensors/ on target devices by
# scripts/maruko_direct_deploy.sh push-isp-bin [NAME].
#
# These are vendor-tuned binary blobs (AE/AWB/CAC/LSC etc.) — there is no
# source build for them. Treat as opaque artifacts; record provenance in
# vendor-libs/maruko/device-info.txt when pulled.
